  collection including an 1828 Webster's dictionary and slang dictionaries
  from the 20th century." data-alt="A selection of dictionaries from the K
 ripke collection including an 1828 Webster's dictionary and slang diction
 aries from the 20th century." src="https://events.iu.edu/live/image/gid/2
 61/width/500/height/333/30107_kripke_collection_photo_2.rev.1771333324.pn
 g" title="kripke collection photo" data-max-w="768" data-max-h="512" load
 ing="lazy" data-optimized="true"/></picture></p>
