DTSTART:20260414T150000Z
DTEND:20260414T170000Z
LOCATION:CHEMISTRY - Room Number: Sciences Library Classroom\, C002R
GEO:39.166131;-86.522581
SUMMARY:Plant & Seed Swap
DESCRIPTION:Our friends from Monroe County Public Library will be on hand
  to share seeds and tell you about their seed swap events. We invited oth
 er community partners who may be on hand to share additional information 
 or resources as well!  While you're here\, take home a succulent courtesy
  of the Sciences Library—no green thumb required. We also encourage any
 one to bring along seeds\, starts\, or cuttings they'd like to pass on to
  a new home.  Come dig in\, swap some starts\, and connect with fellow pl
 ant lovers!
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Our friends from Monroe County Public L
 ibrary will be on hand to share seeds and tell you about their seed swap 
 events. We invited other community partners who may be on hand to share a
 dditional information or resources as well!</p><p>  While you're here\, t
 ake home a succulent courtesy of the Sciences Library—no green thumb re
 quired. We also encourage anyone to bring along seeds\, starts\, or cutti
 ngs they'd like to pass on to a new home.</p><p>  Come dig in\, swap some
  starts\, and connect with fellow plant lovers!</p>
UID:20260414T150000Z-2257090@events.iu.edu
DTSTAMP:20260402T170059Z
URL:https://events.iu.edu/libraries/event/2257090-plant-seed-swap
